// Supabase setup recap:
//   1. Create a project at https://supabase.com
//   2. Copy the Postgres URI from Settings -> Database -> Connection string (Direct)
//   3. Put it in DATABASE_URL in your .env (and in Vercel env vars)
//   4. Run: npx prisma db push   (creates tables)
//   5. Run: npm run db:seed       (sample content)
